# Orbit Axis :: files that must never be uploaded to Vercel (Update 4.0.3).
#
# Everything listed here is either private, local-only, or useless to a
# deployment. Keeping the upload small is a side benefit; the point is that
# private notes and local database state never leave this machine.
#
# .env.local is already excluded by Vercel (it never uploads dotenv files) and
# by .gitignore, and is listed again here so the intent is explicit.

# ── Secrets and local environment ──
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ── Obsidian vault and private project notes ──
07 Orbit App/
docs/
prompts/
.orbit/

# ── Local Supabase stack: config, migrations, seeds, CLI state ──
# Migrations are applied by the owner with the Supabase CLI, never by the app.
supabase/

# ── Tests and fixtures ──
test/

# ── Development tooling ──
.claude/
.github/

# ── Local build/tooling noise ──
node_modules/
*.log
.DS_Store
DESIGN_SYSTEM.md
